Los huéspedes podrán disfrutar de las vistas al centro histórico de Atenas, explorar sus alrededores a su propio ritmo y embarcarse en un viaje de rejuvenecimiento y descubrimiento con un masaje relajante en la sala de masajes etéreo del spa Atenas, sala de vapor, sauna y jacuzzi.

The Greater Columbus Convention Center and Arena District are both less than 2 miles away from the hotel.

description:
Coral Hotel Athens is fully renovated and is located at the Athenian Riviera. It has two private beaches with free loungers and umbrellas for its guests.

It provides mini spa, roof top restaurant and a whirlpool. Only 15 minutes away from Syntagma, Acropolis, Piraeus, Elliniko, Glyfada (driving distance).

The rooms at the Coral Hotel are air-conditioned and feature satellite LCD TV, radio, and work desk. Some of the rooms offer sea views from their balconies.

The Coral Restaurant prepares a traditional Greek breakfast with local products daily while Greek and International dishes are served during lunch and dinner. Vegetarian and vegan menus are also available upon request.

Room service is also available. There is free WiFi access in all hotel areas. Massages are offered by appointment.

Hotel Coral is within walking distance from the commercial centre of Paleo Faliro, with many shopping and entertainment facilities and a waterfront promenade. The Tram across the street connects the Coral with the Athens Metro network. Piraeus Port is a 15-minute drive and El.Venizelos lies within a 40-minute' drive.

description:
Located within 3 km from the Acropolis and close to Metro stations and the business district of Athens, the Athenaeum Intercontinental features award-winning restaurants, a spa centre and a 24-hour gym. The spacious, elegant rooms include marble bathrooms and a seating area.

Featuring wooden furnishings, soft colours and carpets, all rooms at the Athenaeum Intercontinental are equipped with 32’’ LCD satellite TVs, a work desk and coffee maker. Bathrooms are stocked with luxury toiletries, bathrobes and a scale. Some rooms feature artwork by Greek artists and Acropolis views. Executive Lounge is available in some rooms where check in services and breakflast/beverages are available.

The Cafezoe Restaurant serves a rich buffet breakfast, international dishes, as well as Greek favourites. Mediterranean cuisine is served at the award-winning Premiere Restaurant located on the 10th floor, offering spectacular views of the Parthenon and the city of Athens.  A variety of pastries and light meals is served at the fashionable Artlounge.

Guests can swim in the 120m² pool or relax at the hot tub and sauna. Spa treatments include massages, facials, and masks by the exclusive Phytomer range. State-of-the-art Technogym cardiovascular equipment is available at the fitness centre.

The scenic Old Town of Athens, Plaka, is just 1.5 km away.  Ermou shopping area is within 2 km. Eleftherios Venizelos International Airport is at 23 km. Private parking is possible on site.

Las habitaciones del Airotel Alexandros presentan una decoración elegante, WiFi gratuita, TV vía satélite de pantalla plana y set de té y café. Algunas incluyen zona de estar independiente.

El establecimiento también proporciona cada mañana botellas de zumos recién exprimidos, disponibles en la nevera compartida, junto a la cocina abierta. Asimismo, el bar elabora varios tipos de sándwiches y ensaladas saludables para llevar, preparadas a diario en colaboración con un nutricionista. Para el almuerzo y la cena, el restaurante propone especialidades mediterráneas y platos del día acompañados por excelentes vinos locales.

El establecimiento alberga un bar animado en el vestíbulo con prensa, TV, billar y juegos electrónicos. En el vestíbulo también hay un ordenador de uso compartido, cargadores USB e impresoras inalámbricas y, en la entreplanta, se sitúa una sala de reuniones moderna con luz natural y paredes magnéticas. Todos los huéspedes tienen acceso a la playa de Mavili y una piscina de temporada en la azotea (sujeta a disponibilidad).

El Airotel Alexandros se halla a poca distancia del centro comercial Kolonaki y del Museo Benaki. The Concert Hall, the U.S. En las inmediaciones hay numerosas cafeterías y restaurantes. El aparcamiento privado es gratuito.
